|text2     = Reward: Nodes with lower difficulty have infinite Action Value, and enemies will randomly drop the crystal ores as rewards.<br />Battle: Challenging combat Nodes where you will face normal and elite enemies from different competitor factions.<br />Supply: Provides several sets of character and Equipment Supply Packs. You can freely choose supplies based on your current lineup.<br />Encounter: A challenge node with selectable difficulty. You can receive extra rewards after completing the combat challenge. Generally, the higher the difficulty of the enemies challenged, the higher the quality of the rewards you can obtain.<br />Boss: The Boss challenge for the current Plane. Completing the challenge will allow you to clear this Plane.
